item.title: Ninth Custom Tab Block
item.content:
Classic charm combines with edgy femininity in this pair of black trousers from MANGO, exhibiting glossy texture and designed with tapered-leg silhouette. Neatly tailored with a snug-fit zipper closure on the sides and zipper opening on the sides of the hems that render extended opening, this pair of trousers will go well with a ruffled top and stiletto boots.

  • Fitted waist
  • Zipper closure on the side
  • Panelled design on the back knees
  • Glossy texture
  • Ankle length
  • Straight hems
  • Zipper opening on the sides of the hems
